data.description: This charming split-level gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an inviting open floor plan, perfect for family living and entertaining. The second-floor primary bedroom features a small open deck for relaxation. A 3-season room, covered patio, and an 8x10 workshop (with electrical potential) offer versatile spaces for various activities. Enjoy a fenced backyard with a deck off the dining area for outdoor fun. Laundry room comes with washer and dryer. With a brand-new HVAC system, partially finished basement, and an excellent location near Hopewell school, this property is priced right and won't last long. Close to the I-75, shopping and restaurants.
